  "prompt": "What NFL team has the most loyal fans?",
  "response": "Determining which NFL team has the \"most loyal fans\" can be subjective, as loyalty can be measured in different ways, such as attendance at games, merchandise sales, social media engagement, or long-standing support through both good and bad seasons. \n\nHowever, teams often cited for their loyal fanbases include:\n\n- **Green Bay Packers**: Known for their community ownership model, the Packers have a long-standing tradition and a dedicated following, making them one of the most iconic franchises in the league.\n  \n- **Buffalo Bills**: The Bills Mafia is famous for its passionate and dedicated fans, known for their unwavering support even during tough seasons.\n\n- **Pittsburgh Steelers**: The Steelers enjoy a strong and widespread fanbase, often referred to as \"Steeler Nation,\" with support that spans beyond the city of Pittsburgh.\n\n- **Chicago Bears**: With a rich history and a loyal fanbase, the Bears have been a staple in the NFL, and their fans are known for their dedication.\n\nEach of these teams has demonstrated strong fan loyalty for various reasons, but the \"most loyal\" can vary depending on personal perspectives and criteria.",
